Eagle Springs Golf Course and Recreation Center offers two levels of membership with prices for both residents and non-residents of Walton County.
Residents must present a Florida driver's License or Identification Card showing a Walton County address.
A Silver Membership
includes unlimited green fees and unlimited range balls.
A Gold Membership
includes all the benefits of the Silver Membership plus the use of Eagle Springs golf carts and pool access*.
*
Pool is included in the gold membership only
. Pool hours are 10 am to 6 pm. The pool is closed every Tuesday for maintenance.
All memberships are paid monthly on the 1st of the month. Walton County/Walton County School Board employees shall receive a $10/month discount for memberships.
